{"type": "article", "id": 15787, "title": "书架有很多种，有一种是就这样让它倾斜着好了", "description": "在常规事物上稍加改变，就实现了一个新设计。", "date": "2015-10-09T10:51:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2383, "name": "书架"}, {"id": 16877, "name": "倾斜的书架"}, {"id": 767, "name": "家具设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 190, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702124550pQMT7nEtP4mYHB2f.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t设计事务所 <span><a href=\"http://www.objetoptimise.com/\">Objet Optimisé</a> </span>的设计师 <span>Aurélien\r\nVeyrat </span>完成了一个倾斜书架的设计。这个书架叫作“ <span>L </span>书架”，它结构非常简单，可以自行组装。小小的卡口让全书架都倾斜了起来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124544jznbme204sJihfap.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"倾斜的书架\" alt=\"倾斜的书架\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>倾斜的书架</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124545MqCFsfkUZIW32jdH.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"另外一个角度\" alt=\"另外一个角度\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另外一个角度</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124546cd2FvUbBsOkZ3ACe.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"看起来想要倾倒，其实结构非常扎实\" alt=\"看起来想要倾倒，其实结构非常扎实\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>看起来像要倾倒，其实结构非常扎实</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021245464vVydENFMkAsQ3x2.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"细节\" alt=\"细节\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>细节</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124547IVpdBYhGWnHuc4RX.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124547wdSyZ07sVOEzBICb.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"拆卸、搬运起来很方便\" alt=\"拆卸、搬运起来很方便\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>拆卸、搬运起来很方便</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124548gJr4MenQiUtbq1If.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124548iA1gZfl9TUxb0tsJ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" title=\"书架的结构\" alt=\"书架的结构\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>书架的结构</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.objetoptimise.com/en/info\" target=\"_blank\">这个设计机构的网站</a>特别简洁，他们号称绝不设计不实用的东西。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124549NfXugvL6kBSiT0Ca.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"以上是他们设计的椅子\" alt=\"以上是他们设计的椅子\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>以上是他们设计的椅子</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124549eC9fYVn8LFwmX3a2.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"重点是连接部分\" alt=\"重点是连接部分\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>重点是连接部分</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021245508gkUZnE9oYOdahWx.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/06/this-shelf-system-is-made-from-simple-bent-wood-pieces-that-slot-together/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>contemporist</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}